graph LR
    Feast[Feast Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Feast -->|runtime platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.11.3+]
    Feast -->|feature servers| Python[Python 3.11]
    Feast -->|operator build| Go[Go 1.22]
    Feast -->|persistence| Storage[Storage Backend<br/>SQLite/Postgres/Snowflake/S3/GCS/Cassandra]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Feast -.->|external routing| OpenShiftRoutes[OpenShift Routes 4.x]
    Feast -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    Feast -->|custom CA| TrustedCA[odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap Injection]
    Feast -.->|mTLS & traffic mgmt| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio - Optional]
    Feast -.->|user auth| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>OIDC - Optional]

    %% Integration Points
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|metrics scrape| Feast
    OIDC[OIDC Provider] -->|token validation| Feast
    ObjectStorage[S3-compatible Storage] -->|feature data| Feast
    Database[PostgreSQL/Snowflake] -->|feature data| Feast
    Git[Git Repository] -->|feature definitions| Feast
    Cache[Redis/Cassandra/DynamoDB] -->|online store| Feast

    %% Consuming Services (Examples)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| Feast
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -->|SDK calls| Feast
    MLModels[ML Models] -->|inference requests| Feast
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto deploy| Feast

